---
// Harvard Hero — Sobrio, académico, institucional
---

<section class="relative bg-dmk-bg border-b border-dmk-border">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-12 py-16 md:py-20">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
      
      <!-- Foto (3 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-dmk-card border border-dmk-border flex items-center justify-center card-3d">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-dmk-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-dmk-accent">N</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Info (9 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-9 space-y-6">
        
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dmk-text">
            Nicolás Matías Márquez Álvarez
          </h1>
          <p class="font-serif text-lg text-dmk-muted italic">
            PhD in Management, Universidad Adolfo Ibáñez
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px w-24 bg-dmk-accent"></div>

        <p class="font-sans text-base text-dmk-text leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Entrepreneurship and innovation scholar with a PhD in Management. Research focuses on entrepreneurship, SME innovation, sustainability, and the implications of AI for entrepreneurial judgment and innovation governance, with particular attention to Latin American contexts.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-dmk-muted">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-dmk-accent"></span>
            nicolasmarquezalvarez@gmail.com
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-dmk-accent"></span>
            (+56) 930610500
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-dmk-accent"></span>
            Talca, Chile
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Tabs -->
        <div class="flex border-b border-dmk-border pt-4">
          {['Profile', 'Research', 'Teaching', 'Experience', 'Contact'].map((tab, i) => (
            <a href={`#${['','research','teaching','experience','contact'][i]}`} 
               class={`font-sans text-sm px-4 py-2 border-b-2 transition-colors ${i === 0 ? 'border-dmk-accent text-dmk-accent font-semibold' : 'border-transparent text-dmk-muted hover:text-dmk-text'}`}>
              {tab}
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
